<% order = @order %>
<% name = @full_name || "—" %>
<% email = @email || "—" %>

MELISPORTS — INTERNAL ALERT
==================================================

NEW ORDER RECEIVED
Order #<%= order.order_number %>

A new order has been placed on melisports.com and is awaiting fulfilment.
Review the details below and update the order status accordingly.

--------------------------------------------------
ORDER METADATA
--------------------------------------------------
Received: <%= order.created_at.strftime("%Y-%m-%d %H:%M UTC") %>
Status: <%= order.status.humanize %>
Items Count: <%= order.order_items.count %>

--------------------------------------------------
CUSTOMER DETAILS
--------------------------------------------------
Full Name: <%= name %>
Email: <%= email %>
Order ID: #<%= order.order_number %>
Order Date: <%= order.created_at.strftime("%b %-d, %Y") %>

--------------------------------------------------
ITEMS ORDERED
--------------------------------------------------
<% order.order_items.each do |item| %>
- <%= item.product.name %>
  SKU / ID: <%= item.product.id %>
  Qty: <%= item.quantity %>
  Unit Price: ₦<%= number_to_currency(item.amount, unit: "", precision: 2) %>
<% end %>

--------------------------------------------------
ORDER TOTALS
--------------------------------------------------
Subtotal: ₦<%= number_to_currency(order.net_total - order.delivery_fee, unit: "", precision: 2) %>
Delivery Fee: ₦<%= number_to_currency(order.delivery_fee, unit: "", precision: 2) %>
ORDER TOTAL: ₦<%= number_to_currency(order.net_total, unit: "", precision: 2) %>

--------------------------------------------------
DELIVERY ADDRESS
--------------------------------------------------
<%= order.billing_address.street %>
<%= order.billing_address.city %>, <%= order.billing_address.state %> <%= order.billing_address.postal_code %>
NIGERIA

--------------------------------------------------
ACTIONS
--------------------------------------------------
View Order:
melisports-admin/orders/<%= order.order_number %>

Mark as Processing via admin dashboard.

--------------------------------------------------
